<L>And wrapt in weeds the<NOTE N="&sect;" PLACE="foot">The coa&s;t of <HI>Ba$ae;</HI> which was formerly adorned with the works mentioned in the following lines; and where, amid&s;t many magnificent ruins, tho&s;e of a temple erected to <HI>Venus</HI> are &s;till to be &s;een.</NOTE> &s;hore of <HI>Venus</HI> lyes.<MILESTONE N="290"></L>
