<L>Of human kind; what, when depriv'd of ME,</L>
<L>How grievous mu&s;t be thine? In &s;pite of climes,<MILESTONE N="325"></L>
<L>Who&s;e &s;un enliven'd aether wakes the &s;oul</L>
