<L>Then, conde&s;cending kind, the HEAVENLY POWER</L>
<L>Return'd.&mdash;&startq;What here, &s;ugge&s;ted by the &s;cene,<MILESTONE N="360"></L>
<L>I &s;light unfold, record, and &s;ing at home,</L>
