<L>For ever &s;hi$ting runs th' eternal$ round;<MILESTONE N="65"></L>
<L>Thence try'd again&s;t the blood-polluted meal,</L>
<L>And limbs you quivering with &s;ome kindred &s;oul,</L>
<L>To turn the human heart. Delightful truth!</L>
