<L><NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot">The ancient <HI>Sarmatia</HI> contained a va&s;t tract of country, run|ning all along the north of <HI>Europe</HI> and <HI>A&s;ia.</HI></NOTE> <HI>Sarmatia,</HI> travers'd by a thou&s;and &s;treams.<MILESTONE N="515"></L>
