<L>To whom her ruling thunder ocean bears.<MILESTONE N="65"></L>
<L>She too the mineral &s;eeds, th' obedient Lead,</L>
<L>The warlike Iron, nor the peaceful lets,</L>
<L>Forming of life art-civiliz'd the bond;</L>
<L>And<NOTE N="&ast;" PLACE="foot">Tin.</NOTE> that the <HI>Tyrian</HI> merchant &s;ought of old,</L>
<L>Not dreaming then of BRITAIN'S brighter fame.<MILESTONE N="70"></L>
<L>She rears to Freedom an undaunted race:</L>
