<L>On what unyielding ba&s;e? how fini&s;h'd &s;hine?&endq;</L>
<L>At this HER eye, collecting all its fire,</L>
<L>Beam'd more than human; and HER awful voice,</L>
<L><PB N="384" REF="120">
Maje&s;tic thus SHE rais'd&mdash;&startq;To BRITONS bear</L>
<L>This clo&s;ing &s;train, and with inten&s;er note<MILESTONE N="90"></L>
<L>Loud let it &s;ound in their awaken'd ear,</L>
