<L>On PUBLIC VIRTUE, EVERY VIRTUE JOIN'D.</L>
<L>For, lo&s;t this &s;ocial cement of mankind,<MILESTONE N="95"></L>
<L>The greate&s;t empires, by &s;carce-felt degrees,</L>
<L>Will moulder &s;oft away; till, tottering loo&s;e,</L>
<L>They prone at la&s;t. to total ruin ru&s;h.</L>
