<L>Who&s;e &s;treams, from every quarter confluent, form<MILESTONE N="330"></L>
<L>My better <HI>Nile,</HI> that nur&s;es human life.</L>
<L>By rills from thee deduc'd, irrigouus, fed,</L>
<L>The private field looks gay, with Nature's wealth</L>
<L>Abundant flows, and blooms with each delight</L>
<L>That Nature craves. Its happy ma&s;ter there,<MILESTONE N="135"></L>
