<ITEM>Apid&mdash;paid.</ITEM>
<ITEM>Appall&mdash;<HI>affright.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Atween&mdash;<HI>between,</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Ay&mdash;<HI>always.</HI></ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<ITEM>Bale&mdash;<HI>&s;orrow, trouble, misfortune.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Benempt&mdash;<HI>named.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Blazon&mdash;<HI>painting, di&s;playing.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Breme&mdash;<HI>cold, raw.</HI></ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<ITEM>Carol&mdash;<HI>to &s;ing &s;ongs of joy.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Caucus, <HI>the north-ea&s;t wind.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Certes&mdash;<HI>certainly.</HI></ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<ITEM>Dan&mdash;<HI>a word prefixed to names.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Deftly&mdash;<HI>&s;kilfully.</HI></ITEM>
